        {
            "+content": "ふつつかな悪女ではございますが 〜雛宮蝶鼠とりかえ伝〜",
            "+@gid": "656217242",
            "+@type": "Alternative title",
            "+@lang": "JA"
        },
        {
            "+content": "In a kingdom inspired by historical China, five clans put forth their maidens as imperial consorts–but only one will be crowned empress. The frail and beautiful Kou Reirin, the so-called \"butterfly\" of the imperial court, is a shoo-in to marry the crown prince. But when \"court rat\" Shu Keigetsu lashes out at her during the glittering Lantern Festival, it's Reirin who wakes up in the dungeons. Body-swapped by her assailant to steal her position at court, Reirin's plight seems dire...to everyone else. Now that she's got a robust new body, not even the looming threat of execution can stop her.",
            "+@gid": "2425758769",
            "+@type": "Plot Summary"
        },
